{"tid":704257,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國調查：愈來愈多人棄Facebook看新聞, 轉投WhatsApp","createTime":"2018-06-16T10:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T14:47:53.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"daec1916c89e04ec52100f9f6f1f325d26203643","tid":704257,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"其實香港都係咁  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://inews.hket.com/article/2095856/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2095856%2F&d=cUk%2FhtErB3%2FWPGqoGfB84IS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=0cd4dae9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://inews.hket.com/article/2095856/</a><br />\n<br />\n調查：愈來愈多人棄Facebook看新聞 轉投WhatsApp<br />\n 國際 16:43 2018/06/15  <br />\n    <br />\n<strong>最新調查發現，使用Facebook閱讀新聞的美國用戶人數正在下降，當中以年輕用戶最顯著，不少人轉投WhatsApp或Snapchat等即時通訊程式。</strong><br />\n<br />\n英國牛津大學的路透新聞學研究所（Reuters Institute for the Study of Journalism）委託YouGov，調查37個地區的7.4萬名用戶，發現2016年至今，美國以Facebook看新聞的人數下跌6%， 2017年至2018年間跌勢加劇至9%，年輕用戶更跌20%。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，透過facebook 旗下的WhatsApp及Instagram看新聞的人數則在兩年間分別上升4%及3%；Snapchat亦上升2%。<br />\n<br />\n研究中心指，用戶轉投WhatsApp等通訊程式是因為它們的隱密性高，令他們能夠放心分享新聞並暢所欲言；相反Facebook是相對公開的平台，隨着朋友網絡愈來愈大，令用戶有所顧忌。"},{"pid":"75434c776c6ba5677e7aebf53a6374e75bb968e8","tid":704257,"uid":156618,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:12:18.000Z","msg":"Whatsapp 咪又係Facebook <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a20be99d6a277c9118e06a86714c68be306722e","tid":704257,"uid":52358,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:13:24.000Z","msg":"長輩圖<br />\n廢老啲千字文<br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d18b8bb8a80c450705f7e09ba026ab01cc68aa","tid":704257,"uid":2959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"Whatsapp同ig都係Faceb